'''NGC 588''' 是[[三角座|三角座]]的一個[[星系|星系]]。它是由德国-丹麦天文学家[[罗雷尔·路德威·德亚瑞司特|罗雷尔·路德威·德亚瑞司特]]於1861年10月2日发现。它的赤經為1時32分45.7秒，赤緯為30°38'56"，星等為13.5<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dso-browser.com/deep-sky/1480/ngc-588/diffuse-nebula|title=Diffuse nebula NGC 588 · Deep Sky Objects Browser|last=Rojas|first=Sebastián García|website=DSO Browser|language=en|access-date=2017-05-12|archive-date=2018-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180101194154/https://dso-browser.com/deep-sky/1480/ngc-588/diffuse-nebula}}</ref><ref name=SIMBAD>{{Cite web|url=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?mescat.iras=on&mescat.iso=on&mescat.iue=on&Ident=@1522773&Name=NGC+++588&submit=display+selected+measurements#lab_meas|title=NGC 588|website=simbad.u-strasbg.fr|access-date=2017-05-14|archive-date=2018-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180101194318/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?mescat.iras=on&mescat.iso=on&mescat.iue=on&Ident=@1522773&Name=NGC+++588&submit=display+selected+measurements#lab_meas}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc5a.htm#588|title=New General Catalog Objects: NGC 550 - 599|website=cseligman.com|language=en-US|access-date=2017-05-12|archive-date=2015-07-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6aJ6YU1ad?url=http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc5a.htm#588}}</ref>。

